{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"progress","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)progress","symbolKind":"property"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The pack’s current progress."}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"readonly","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-requestProgress","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":"s about this pack that come from the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"default notification center.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}],"title":"MLNOfflinePack","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgress":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A structure containing information about an offline pack’s current download"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"progress.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogress","title":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflineStorage"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Posted by the shared ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object when an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"whenever any field in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"text":" property changes.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification","title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/progress":{"title":"progress","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The pack’s current progress."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","fragments":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress","type":"topic"}}}